@startuml
title TRAVELBUDDY Recommendation Summary Sequence

actor User
participant "Controller" as Controller
participant "Recommendation Service" as Service
database "Database" as DB
participant "AI Service (Groq)" as AI

User -> Controller: Submit AI Suggestions form
Controller -> Service: Build recommendations
Service -> DB: Query flights/hotels/preferences
DB --> Service: Matching data
Service -> AI: Generate natural-language summary
AI --> Service: Summary text
Service --> Controller: Recommendations + summary
Controller --> User: Render results page

@enduml
